data.description: Come view this immaculate Pool Home located in the heart of Valrico. This spacious 4-bedroom 2-bathroom 2 car garage home which offers vaulted ceilings, open floor plan, beautiful gourmet kitchen that features Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a large kitchen Island. This is the perfect kitchen if you enjoy cooking or eating.  There is a separate formal dining area for any occasion or family gatherings. The primary suite has ample room with a walk-in closet, huge master bathroom with beautiful cabinets and counter tops, large garden tub, dual sinks and a separate shower. After a long day you can leave your master suite through the sliding glass doors to enjoy the heated pool and spa inside the enclosed lanai. There are three other sizeable bedrooms with lots of closet space. This home is meticulously maintained! Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Get the opportunity to enjoy a quiet community with access to top-rated schools and close proximity to plenty of shopping, dining, and entertainment options.
